{
  "video_id": "YA87VEeoZLI",
  "title": "Henry Lin: What we can learn from galaxies far, far away",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12934.0,
      "end_time": 16268.0,
      "text": "Here are some images of clusters of galaxies."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16268.0,
      "end_time": 18101.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re exactly what they sound like."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18101.0,
      "end_time": 20654.0,
      "text": "They are these huge collections of galaxies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20654.0,
      "end_time": 22909.0,
      "text": "bound together by their mutual gravity."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22909.0,
      "end_time": 25570.0,
      "text": "So most of the points that you see on the screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25571.0,
      "end_time": 28100.0,
      "text": "are not individual stars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28100.0,
      "end_time": 30936.0,
      "text": "but collections of stars, or galaxies."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30936.0,
      "end_time": 33267.0,
      "text": "Now, by showing you some of these images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33267.0,
      "end_time": 35140.0,
      "text": "I hope that you will quickly see that"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35140.0,
      "end_time": 37694.0,
      "text": "galaxy clusters are these beautiful objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37694.0,
      "end_time": 39187.0,
      "text": "but more than that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39187.0,
      "end_time": 41849.0,
      "text": "I think galaxy clusters are mysterious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41850.0,
      "end_time": 43403.0,
      "text": "they are surprising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43403.0,
      "end_time": 44820.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44820.0,
      "end_time": 48351.0,
      "text": "Useful as the universe&#39;s most massive laboratories."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48351.0,
      "end_time": 51987.0,
      "text": "And as laboratories, to describe galaxy clusters"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51987.0,
      "end_time": 53852.0,
      "text": "is to describe the experiments"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53852.0,
      "end_time": 55404.0,
      "text": "that you can do with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55405.0,
      "end_time": 57685.0,
      "text": "And I think there are four major types,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57685.0,
      "end_time": 60269.0,
      "text": "and the first type that I want to describe"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60269.0,
      "end_time": 62488.0,
      "text": "is probing the very big."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62488.0,
      "end_time": 64182.0,
      "text": "So, how big?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64183.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68434.0,
      "text": "Well, here is an image of a particular galaxy cluster."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68434.0,
      "end_time": 71402.0,
      "text": "It is so massive that the light passing through it"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71403.0,
      "end_time": 74180.0,
      "text": "is being bent, it&#39;s being distorted"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74180.0,
      "end_time": 76527.0,
      "text": "by the extreme gravity of this cluster."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76527.0,
      "end_time": 78331.0,
      "text": "And, in fact, if you look very carefully"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78331.0,
      "end_time": 81310.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll be able to see rings around this cluster."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81310.0,
      "end_time": 82580.0,
      "text": "Now, to give you a number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82580.0,
      "end_time": 84363.0,
      "text": "this particular galaxy cluster"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84363.0,
      "end_time": 88571.0,
      "text": "has a mass of over one million billion suns."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88571.0,
      "end_time": 91884.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just mind-boggling how  massive these systems can get."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91884.0,
      "end_time": 93385.0,
      "text": "But more than their mass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93385.0,
      "end_time": 95359.0,
      "text": "they have this additional feature."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95359.0,
      "end_time": 97702.0,
      "text": "They are essentially isolated systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97703.0,
      "end_time": 99925.0,
      "text": "so if we like, we can think of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 99925.0,
      "end_time": 103195.0,
      "text": "as a scaled-down version of the entire universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103195.0,
      "end_time": 105196.0,
      "text": "And many of the questions that we might have"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105197.0,
      "end_time": 107165.0,
      "text": "about the universe at large scales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107165.0,
      "end_time": 109800.0,
      "text": "such as, how does gravity work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 109800.0,
      "end_time": 112112.0,
      "text": "might be answered by studying these systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112112.0,
      "end_time": 113445.0,
      "text": "So that was very big."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113445.0,
      "end_time": 115330.0,
      "text": "The second things is very hot."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 115330.0,
      "end_time": 118113.0,
      "text": "Okay, if I take an image of a galaxy cluster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118113.0,
      "end_time": 121300.0,
      "text": "and I subtract away all of the starlight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121300.0,
      "end_time": 123825.0,
      "text": "what I&#39;m left with is this big, blue blob."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123825.0,
      "end_time": 125310.0,
      "text": "This is in false color."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125310.0,
      "end_time": 127659.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually X-ray light that we&#39;re seeing."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127659.0,
      "end_time": 130320.0,
      "text": "And the question is, if it&#39;s not galaxies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130320.0,
      "end_time": 132519.0,
      "text": "what is emitting this light?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 132519.0,
      "end_time": 134419.0,
      "text": "The answer is hot gas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 134419.0,
      "end_time": 136242.0,
      "text": "million-degree gas --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 136242.0,
      "end_time": 137899.0,
      "text": "in fact, it&#39;s plasma."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 137899.0,
      "end_time": 139558.0,
      "text": "And the reason why it&#39;s so hot"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 139558.0,
      "end_time": 141537.0,
      "text": "goes back to the previous slide."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 141538.0,
      "end_time": 144278.0,
      "text": "The extreme gravity of these systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144278.0,
      "end_time": 147320.0,
      "text": "is accelerating particles of gas to great speeds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 147320.0,
      "end_time": 149902.0,
      "text": "and great speeds means great temperatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 149902.0,
      "end_time": 151620.0,
      "text": "So this is the main idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 151621.0,
      "end_time": 153987.0,
      "text": "but science is a rough draft."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 153987.0,
      "end_time": 156537.0,
      "text": "There are many basic properties about this plasma"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 156538.0,
      "end_time": 158236.0,
      "text": "that still confuse us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 158236.0,
      "end_time": 159569.0,
      "text": "still puzzle us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159569.0,
      "end_time": 161655.0,
      "text": "and still push our understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161655.0,
      "end_time": 163694.0,
      "text": "of the physics of the very hot."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 163694.0,
      "end_time": 167120.0,
      "text": "Third thing: probing the very small."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167121.0,
      "end_time": 169967.0,
      "text": "Now, to explain this, I need to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169967.0,
      "end_time": 171987.0,
      "text": "a very disturbing fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171987.0,
      "end_time": 174777.0,
      "text": "Most of the universe&#39;s matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174777.0,
      "end_time": 176588.0,
      "text": "is not made up of atoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 176588.0,
      "end_time": 178537.0,
      "text": "You were lied to."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 178538.0,
      "end_time": 181665.0,
      "text": "Most of it is made up of something  very, very mysterious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 181665.0,
      "end_time": 183786.0,
      "text": "which we call dark matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 183787.0,
      "end_time": 187454.0,
      "text": "Dark matter is something that  doesn&#39;t like to interact very much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 187454.0,
      "end_time": 189122.0,
      "text": "except through gravity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 189122.0,
      "end_time": 190734.0,
      "text": "and of course we would like to learn more about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 190734.0,
      "end_time": 192277.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a particle physicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 192277.0,
      "end_time": 194785.0,
      "text": "you want to know what happens  when we smash things together."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 194786.0,
      "end_time": 196776.0,
      "text": "And dark matter is no exception."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 196776.0,
      "end_time": 198436.0,
      "text": "Well, how do we do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 198436.0,
      "end_time": 199927.0,
      "text": "To answer that question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 199927.0,
      "end_time": 201320.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to have to ask another one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 201320.0,
      "end_time": 204486.0,
      "text": "which is, what happens when galaxy clusters collide?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 204486.0,
      "end_time": 206796.0,
      "text": "Here is an image."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 206796.0,
      "end_time": 209987.0,
      "text": "Since galaxy clusters are representative"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 209987.0,
      "end_time": 213111.0,
      "text": "slices of the universe, scaled-down versions."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 213111.0,
      "end_time": 215233.0,
      "text": "They are mostly made up of dark matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 215234.0,
      "end_time": 217787.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s what you see in this bluish purple."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 217787.0,
      "end_time": 219404.0,
      "text": "The red represents the hot gas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 219404.0,
      "end_time": 221371.0,
      "text": "and, of course, you can see many galaxies."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 221371.0,
      "end_time": 223736.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s happened is a particle accelerator"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 223736.0,
      "end_time": 225626.0,
      "text": "at a huge, huge scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 225627.0,
      "end_time": 227404.0,
      "text": "And this is very important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 227404.0,
      "end_time": 229287.0,
      "text": "because what it means is that very, very small"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 229287.0,
      "end_time": 232371.0,
      "text": "effects that might be difficult to detect in the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 232371.0,
      "end_time": 234550.0,
      "text": "might be compounded and compounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 234550.0,
      "end_time": 238359.0,
      "text": "into something that we could  possibly observe in nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 238359.0,
      "end_time": 239871.0,
      "text": "So, it&#39;s very funny."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 239871.0,
      "end_time": 241819.0,
      "text": "The reason why galaxy clusters"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 241819.0,
      "end_time": 243484.0,
      "text": "can teach us about dark matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 243485.0,
      "end_time": 245235.0,
      "text": "the reason why galaxy clusters"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 245235.0,
      "end_time": 247788.0,
      "text": "can teach us about the physics of the very small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 247788.0,
      "end_time": 250819.0,
      "text": "is precisely because they are so very big."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 250819.0,
      "end_time": 254904.0,
      "text": "Fourth thing: the physics of the very strange."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 254904.0,
      "end_time": 257954.0,
      "text": "Certainly what I&#39;ve said so far is crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 257954.0,
      "end_time": 260237.0,
      "text": "Okay, if there&#39;s anything stranger"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 260237.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262654.0,
      "text": "I think it has to be dark energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 262654.0,
      "end_time": 264371.0,
      "text": "If I throw a ball into the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 264371.0,
      "end_time": 266169.0,
      "text": "I expect it to go up."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 266169.0,
      "end_time": 268293.0,
      "text": "What I don&#39;t expect is that it go up"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 268293.0,
      "end_time": 270459.0,
      "text": "at an ever-increasing rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 270459.0,
      "end_time": 273204.0,
      "text": "Similarly, cosmologists understand why"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 273204.0,
      "end_time": 274786.0,
      "text": "the universe is expanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 274786.0,
      "end_time": 276954.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t understand why it&#39;s expanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 276954.0,
      "end_time": 278892.0,
      "text": "at an ever-increasing rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 278892.0,
      "end_time": 280570.0,
      "text": "They give the cause of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 280570.0,
      "end_time": 282162.0,
      "text": "accelerated expansion a name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 282162.0,
      "end_time": 284460.0,
      "text": "and they call it dark energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 284460.0,
      "end_time": 286734.0,
      "text": "And, again, we want to learn more about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 286734.0,
      "end_time": 289121.0,
      "text": "So, one particular question that we have is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 289121.0,
      "end_time": 291816.0,
      "text": "how does dark energy affect the universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 291816.0,
      "end_time": 293433.0,
      "text": "at the largest scales?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 293434.0,
      "end_time": 294893.0,
      "text": "Depending on how strong it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 294893.0,
      "end_time": 298154.0,
      "text": "maybe structure forms faster or slower."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 298154.0,
      "end_time": 300703.0,
      "text": "Well, the problem with the large-scale structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 300703.0,
      "end_time": 303410.0,
      "text": "of the universe is that it&#39;s horribly complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 303410.0,
      "end_time": 305370.0,
      "text": "Here is a computer simulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 305370.0,
      "end_time": 307498.0,
      "text": "And we need a way to simplify it."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 307498.0,
      "end_time": 311690.0,
      "text": "Well, I like to think about this using an analogy."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 311690.0,
      "end_time": 313787.0,
      "text": "If I want to understand the sinking of the Titanic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 313787.0,
      "end_time": 315453.0,
      "text": "the most important thing to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 315453.0,
      "end_time": 317234.0,
      "text": "is not to model the little positions"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 317234.0,
      "end_time": 320155.0,
      "text": "of every single little piece of the boat that broke off."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 320155.0,
      "end_time": 321820.0,
      "text": "The most important thing to do is"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 321820.0,
      "end_time": 323820.0,
      "text": "to track the two biggest parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 323821.0,
      "end_time": 327653.0,
      "text": "Similarly, I can learn a lot about the universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 327653.0,
      "end_time": 329120.0,
      "text": "at the largest scales"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 329120.0,
      "end_time": 330871.0,
      "text": "by tracking its biggest pieces"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 330871.0,
      "end_time": 334861.0,
      "text": "and those biggest pieces are clusters of galaxies."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 334862.0,
      "end_time": 337818.0,
      "text": "So, as I come to a close,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 337818.0,
      "end_time": 339820.0,
      "text": "you might feel slightly cheated."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 339820.0,
      "end_time": 342700.0,
      "text": "I mean, I began by talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 342700.0,
      "end_time": 344153.0,
      "text": "how galaxy clusters are useful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 344153.0,
      "end_time": 345653.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve given some reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 345653.0,
      "end_time": 348253.0,
      "text": "but what is their use really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 348253.0,
      "end_time": 350370.0,
      "text": "Well, to answer this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 350370.0,
      "end_time": 352986.0,
      "text": "I want to give you a quote by Henry Ford"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 352986.0,
      "end_time": 354472.0,
      "text": "when he was asked about cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 354472.0,
      "end_time": 355830.0,
      "text": "He had this to say:"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 355831.0,
      "end_time": 358120.0,
      "text": "\"If I had asked people what they wanted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 358120.0,
      "end_time": 360903.0,
      "text": "they would have said faster horses.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 360903.0,
      "end_time": 363404.0,
      "text": "Today, we as a society are faced"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 363404.0,
      "end_time": 365622.0,
      "text": "with many, many difficult problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 365622.0,
      "end_time": 369453.0,
      "text": "And the solutions to these  problems are not obvious."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 369453.0,
      "end_time": 371619.0,
      "text": "They are not faster horses."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 371620.0,
      "end_time": 373862.0,
      "text": "They will require an enormous amount of"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 373862.0,
      "end_time": 375568.0,
      "text": "scientific ingenuity."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 375568.0,
      "end_time": 377154.0,
      "text": "So, yes, we need to focus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 377154.0,
      "end_time": 378904.0,
      "text": "yes, we need to concentrate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 378904.0,
      "end_time": 380870.0,
      "text": "but we also need to remember that"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 380870.0,
      "end_time": 383705.0,
      "text": "innovation, ingenuity, inspiration --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 383705.0,
      "end_time": 385370.0,
      "text": "these things come"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 385370.0,
      "end_time": 386724.0,
      "text": "when we broaden our field of vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 386725.0,
      "end_time": 388650.0,
      "text": "when we step back"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 388650.0,
      "end_time": 389414.0,
      "text": "when we zoom out."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 389414.0,
      "end_time": 391236.0,
      "text": "And I can&#39;t think of a better way to do this than"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 391237.0,
      "end_time": 394992.0,
      "text": "by studying the universe around us. Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 394992.0,
      "end_time": 397941.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}